object.script:
x=0 y=0 z=0 k=0 set1=0 set2=0 consumptHour=0 per100kph=0 fuel=0 absConsumptHout=0 consumptMin = 0 minToFill = 0 consumptSec = 0 dist=1 function onTick()
speed = input.getNumber(11) fluidLvl = input.getNumber(12) capacity = input.getNumber(13) dist = math.min(input.getNumber(14),2) measurement = input.getNumber(15)
percent = fluidLvl / capacity
convert = {{0.001,1,"km","m"}, {0.001609,3.281,"mi","ft"}}
if x ~= 601 then x=x+1 y=y+fluidLvl z=z+fluidLvl end
if x == 300 then set1 = z/600 z=0 end
if x == 600 then set2 = y/600 consumptHour=math.floor((set1-set2)*720) fuel = math.floor(set2) absConsumptHout = math.abs(consumptHour) consumptMin=math.floor(math.abs((set1-set2)*12)) consumptSec=math.floor((math.abs((set1-set2)/5))*100)/100 minToFill = math.floor(math.abs((capacity-set2) / consumptMin)) -- Time Remaining = Fuel / Consumption (s) -- Time(in seconds) timeRemaining = (fluidLvl / consumptSec) timeRemainingHrs = math.floor(timeRemaining/3600) timeRemainingMin = math.floor(timeRemaining/60-(timeRemainingHrs*60)) timeRemainingSec = math.floor(timeRemaining - timeRemainingHrs*3600 - timeRemainingMin*60) -- Distance Remaining = fuel time(s) * speed -- Range(in meters) distRemaining = timeRemaining * speed distRemainingKM = distRemaining/1000 distRemainingMI = distRemainingKM*1.609 x=0 y=0 end
if k ~= 1200 then k=k+1 end
inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
isPressingRectangle = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 1, 12, 64, 14) output.setBool(1, isPressingRectangle) end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() if k == 1200 then
screen.setColor(10, 10, 10) screen.drawRectF(0, 12, 64, 41)
if isPressingRectangle then screen.setColor(20, 20, 20) screen.drawRectF(0, 12, 64, 13) end
screen.setColor(70, 70, 70) screen.drawTextBox(2, 2, 60, 5, "remaining", 0, 0)
screen.setColor(10, 10, 10) screen.drawRectF(3, 9, 59, 2)
screen.setColor(20, 20, 20) screen.drawRectF(((x/600)*58)+2, 9, 2, 2)
screen.setColor(40, 40, 40) screen.drawRect(2, 8, 59, 3) screen.drawLine(0, 11, 64, 11) -- TITLE 1: 2,13 | 2,19 -- TITLE 2: 2,27 | 2,33
screen.setColor(70, 70, 70) screen.drawText(2,27, "TIME") screen.setColor(27, 70, 12) if timeRemainingSec > 1 then -- Time remaining timeRemainingFormat = string.format("%02d:%02d:%02d",math.min(timeRemainingHrs,99),math.min(timeRemainingMin,59),math.min(timeRemainingSec,59)) screen.drawText(2,33, timeRemainingFormat) if speed > 5 then screen.drawText(2,19, string.format("%04.2f"..convert[measurement][2+dist],distRemaining*convert[measurement][dist])) else screen.drawText(2,19, "0000km") end else screen.drawText(2,19, "0000"..convert[measurement][2+dist]) screen.drawText(2,33, "00:00:00") end screen.setColor(40, 40, 40) screen.drawLine(0, 25, 64, 25) screen.drawLine(56, 14, 60, 18) screen.drawLine(56, 22, 61, 17)
screen.setColor(70, 70, 70) if consumptHour < -30 then screen.drawText(2, 27, "FILL MIN") screen.setColor(27, 70, 12) screen.drawText(2, 33, minToFill) else screen.drawText(2,13, "DISTANCE") screen.setColor(27, 70, 12) end
screen.setColor(40, 40, 40) screen.drawLine(0, 39, 64, 39)
screen.setColor(70, 70, 70) screen.drawText(2, 41, "FUEL L") screen.setColor(27, 70, 12) screen.drawText(2, 47, fuel) screen.setColor(40, 40, 40) screen.drawLine(0, 53, 64, 53)
screen.drawRect(2, 53, 59, 8) screen.setColor(20, 20, 20) screen.drawRect(3, 54, 57, 6) screen.setColor(10, 27, 4) screen.drawRectF(4, 55, percent*56, 5)
else screen.drawTextBox(2, 27, 60, 5, "loading", 0, 0) screen.drawRect(2, 33, 59, 8) screen.setColor(12, 20, 70) screen.drawRectF(3, 34, (k/1200)*58, 7) end end

node.label: Input
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

object.script:
s=screen s.dt=s.drawText i=input i.gn=i.getNumber s.sc=s.setColor
x=0 y=0 z=0 k=0 set1=0 set2=0 consumptHour=0 per100kph=0 fuel=0 absConsumptHout=0 consumptMin = 0 minToFill = 0 consumptSec = 0 time=1 function onTick()
speed = i.gn(11) fluidLvl = i.gn(12) capacity = i.gn(13) time = i.gn(14) distance = i.gn(15)
percent = fluidLvl / capacity
if distance == 1 then convert = 3.6 elseif distance == 2 then convert = 2.236936 elseif distance == 3 then convert = 1.943844 end
if x ~= 601 then x=x+1 y=y+fluidLvl z=z+fluidLvl end
if x == 300 then set1 = z/600 z=0 end
if x == 600 then set2 = y/600 consumptHour=math.floor((set1-set2)*720) per100kph = math.floor(consumptHour/((speed*convert)/100)) fuel = math.floor(set2) absConsumptHout = math.abs(consumptHour)
consumptMin=math.floor(math.abs((set1-set2)*12)) consumptSec=math.floor((math.abs((set1-set2)/5))*10)/10 minToFill = math.floor(math.abs((capacity-set2) / consumptMin)) x=0 y=0 end
if k ~= 1200 then k=k+1 end
inputX = i.gn(3) inputY = i.gn(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
isPressingRectangle = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 0, 32, 12) output.setBool(1, isPressingRectangle)
end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() if k == 1200 then
s.sc(10, 10, 10) s.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 27)
if isPressingRectangle then s.sc(20, 20, 20) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 33, 13) end
s.sc(10, 10, 10) s.drawRectF(3, 28, 26, 2) s.sc(10, 25, 4) --s.drawRectF(3, 28, percent*26, 2) s.drawRectF(3, 28, percent*18, 2)
s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.drawRectF(((x/600)*26)+2, 28, 2, 2)
s.sc(40, 40, 40) s.drawRect(2, 27, 27, 3) s.drawLine(0, 27, 32, 27)
s.sc(70, 70, 70) if time == 1 then s.dt(1, 1, " HOUR") elseif time == 2 then s.dt(1, 1, " MIN") elseif time == 3 then s.dt(1, 1, " SEC") end
s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 1, " >")
if consumptHour < -20 or consumptHour > 20 then if time == 1 then if absConsumptHout < 99999 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, absConsumptHout .. "L") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, absConsumptHout) else s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, math.floor(absConsumptHout/1000) .. "T") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, math.floor(absConsumptHout/1000)) end elseif time == 2 then if consumptMin < 99999 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, consumptMin .. "L") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, consumptMin) else s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, math.floor(consumptMin/1000) .. "T") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, math.floor(consumptMin/1000)) end elseif time == 3 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, consumptSec .. "L") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, consumptSec) end else s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(2, 7, "--") end s.sc(40, 40, 40) s.drawLine(0, 13, 32, 13)
s.sc(70, 70, 70) if consumptHour < -30 then s.dt(1, 15, "FILL") s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 21, minToFill.."m") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 21, minToFill)
else if convert == 3.6 then s.dt(1, 15, "100 KM") elseif convert == 2.236936 then s.dt(1, 15, "100 mi") elseif convert == 1.943844 then s.dt(1, 15, "100 Kt") end
if speed > 5 then if per100kph < 99999 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 21, per100kph.."L") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 21, per100kph) else s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 21, math.floor(per100kph/100) .."T") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 21, math.floor(per100kph/100)) end else s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(2, 21, "--") end end
else s.drawTextBox(0, 7, 32, 5, "load", 0, 0) s.drawRect(2, 13, 27, 8) s.sc(12, 20, 70) s.drawRectF(3, 14, (k/1200)*25, 7) end end
